UK: From BBC online
<http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/2858439.stm>
A British man returning from Hong Kong has been admitted to hospital with a
suspected case - the UK's first. [from another newswire there was
additional information on this case: The suspected case is a man who
travelled from Hong Kong to Manchester via Amsterdam on Saturday. He is now
being treated in isolation at the Infectious Diseases Unit at North
Manchester General Hospital.]
